      "comment": "COME ON LUBA (1) is racing well without winning, recording three minors on end, the latest hitting the ground running with a fast early sectional but finishing in the minors again when third (22.78) over 400m at this track. Top prospect. EDIE MONSOON (7) charged out of the boxes with a strong early sectional but swamped late when a close up fourth (22.86) at this track over 400m. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. SPRING ESPRESSO (6) was well fancied to win maiden two back then finished third last start (20.12) at Traralgon over 350m. Expected to feature on best form. CLEAR SLATE (3) is a chance after six-and-a-half weeks.",
